# Per-domain generated state — clod regenerates this on every run.
*/.clod/system/
*/.clod/runtime*/
*/.clod/id

# Per-tool state — host credentials / sessions / model blobs land
# here and shouldn't be checked in.
*/.clod/claude/
*/.clod/crush/
*/.clod/tool

# clod settings the user can flip locally.
*/.clod/concurrent
*/.clod/ssh
*/.clod/gpus
*/.clod/claude-default-flags

# Default Dockerfile_user/Dockerfile_project clod writes are
# stub examples; only commit them when a domain actually needs
# customisation. The random/ domain is meant to stay vanilla.
*/.clod/Dockerfile_user
*/.clod/Dockerfile_project
